01:18:05.000 --> 01:18:08.000
And finally, the penultimate criterion.

01:18:08.000 --> 01:18:11.000
It is necessary to avoid intermediate strategies.

01:18:11.000 --> 01:18:16.000
Strategies that arise when trying to follow two opposite strategies at the same time.

01:18:16.000 --> 01:18:19.000
For example.

01:18:19.000 --> 01:18:26.000
