01:19:46.000 --> 01:19:52.000
Setting the goal of becoming the first in the industry is probably not the right thing to do.

01:19:52.000 --> 01:20:01.000
The fact is that it is easier to spend effort to fight with competitors in the same niche.

01:20:01.000 --> 01:20:08.000
