01:29:07.000 --> 01:29:17.000
The company has more than 40 targets.

01:29:17.000 --> 01:29:24.000
Each of these 40 targets has about 7-10 indicators.

01:29:24.000 --> 01:29:27.000
Let's take 10 for the sake of simplicity.

01:29:27.000 --> 01:29:30.000
This means 400 management objects.

01:29:30.000 --> 01:29:36.000
All these management objects are interconnected.

01:29:36.000 --> 01:29:39.000
Such a system loses its management.

01:29:39.000 --> 01:29:47.000
And, in principle, it turned out that a significant number of indicators were used at each level.

01:29:47.000 --> 01:29:50.000
A much more limited number.

01:29:50.000 --> 01:29:56.000
The next typical mistake is the establishment of unattainable goals.

01:29:57.000 --> 01:30:06.000
The unattainability of the goal stimulates the behavior of employees of different hierarchies.

01:30:06.000 --> 01:30:14.000
They should lower their hands, because these goals cannot be achieved anyway.

01:30:14.000 --> 01:30:22.000
Why make an effort to an unattainable goal?

01:30:23.000 --> 01:30:26.000
Therefore, the strategy is not implemented.

01:30:27.000 --> 01:30:32.000
The next typical mistake is the compatibility with existing control systems.

01:30:32.000 --> 01:30:35.000
The implementation of the strategy must be monitored.

01:30:35.000 --> 01:30:44.000
It is necessary to carry out a plan-fact analysis of the performance of indicators

01:30:44.000 --> 01:30:51.000
and the achievement of the target values of these indicators for each allocated and decomposed strategic goal.

01:30:51.000 --> 01:30:58.000
Accordingly, some reaper points should be designated, according to which the control is carried out.

01:30:58.000 --> 01:31:08.000
If at the moment the company does not have control systems that are ready to remove the values of the indicators,

01:31:09.000 --> 01:31:14.000
it is impossible to correct the strategy and it can become an inadequate situation.

01:31:14.000 --> 01:31:25.000
And, accordingly, the inadequacy of the real situation, both inside the company and in its external environment,

01:31:25.000 --> 01:31:35.000
that is, the strategy that the company implements, can lead to the most deplorable results for the company.

01:31:35.000 --> 01:31:48.000
The competence of the employees should be trained and prepared to start implementing the strategy.

01:31:48.000 --> 01:31:56.000
