01:32:11.000 --> 01:32:19.000
and a vertical decomposition of the goals within the organizational structure of the company,

01:32:20.000 --> 01:32:29.000
which, in fact, leads to the movement in the wrong direction, which was planned when developing the strategy.

01:32:29.000 --> 01:32:37.000
And finally, the last and most important typical mistake is to bring the situation to a significant resistance to changes.

01:32:38.000 --> 01:32:48.000
In a separate module dedicated to the management of organizational changes, you will consider this problem.

01:32:48.000 --> 01:33:00.000
I can tell you that if during the implementation of any organizational changes, including the development and implementation of the strategy,

01:33:01.000 --> 01:33:17.000
we do not observe any positive moments in three months, we can bury all our beginnings, because then the resistance to changes will increase.

01:33:17.000 --> 01:33:24.000
Moreover, I will remind you of the classic saying, a kind word and a cat is pleased.

01:33:24.000 --> 01:33:34.000
