01:33:55.000 --> 01:33:59.000
Let's consider an example of the development of a strategy by a group of companies.

01:33:59.000 --> 01:34:07.000
The company is Russian, it is engaged in metallurgy.

01:34:07.000 --> 01:34:15.000
For this company, a project was carried out on the development of a strategy for the establishment of a strategic planning system,

01:34:15.000 --> 01:34:19.000
on the development and implementation of a system of balanced indicators.

01:34:20.000 --> 01:34:29.000
The project was accompanied by the implementation of the ERP system as information support, and a design office was also created within the framework of the project.

01:34:30.000 --> 01:34:37.000
As for the company, the company is the leader in the ferroalloy market in Russia.

01:34:37.000 --> 01:34:48.000
The key indicators that the company had at the beginning of the project were the annual turnover of 200 million, the market share of 25%.

01:34:48.000 --> 01:34:54.000
What problems preceded the project? Why was the project started?

01:34:54.000 --> 01:35:03.000
The company lacked a systematic approach to decision-making, it lacked planning of movement and achievement of strategic goals,

01:35:03.000 --> 01:35:09.000
and the company realized the imperfection of the ERP system.

01:35:10.000 --> 01:35:22.000
The project was carried out under the framework of strategic diagnostics.

01:35:22.000 --> 01:35:34.000
During the strategic diagnostics, a group of stakeholders was identified, strategic goals were set and the company's vision was determined.

01:35:34.000 --> 01:35:45.000
Then a strategy was developed, which was reflected in two documents, namely the Strategy Act and the Corporate Culture Code.

01:35:45.000 --> 01:35:57.000
Within the framework of the development of a decomposition of the strategy at all levels, at the level of business units and individual units of the company,

01:35:57.000 --> 01:36:12.000
master plans of strategic events, strategic maps for each unit were developed, and indicators of achievement of these goals,

01:36:12.000 --> 01:36:17.000
indicators of achievement of goals entered into the strategic maps of the unit were established.

01:36:18.000 --> 01:36:34.000
At the same time, a motivation system was set up, a bonus calculation system was developed, a regulation of adjusting the balanced indicator system was developed,

01:36:34.000 --> 01:36:38.000
and an implementation audit was also carried out.

01:36:38.000 --> 01:36:47.000
Thus, the stages of the project were first developed by the corporate strategy, then the development of a balanced indicator system,

01:36:47.000 --> 01:36:53.000
then the optimization of business processes and the setting up of a motivation system and a control system,

01:36:53.000 --> 01:37:04.000
simultaneously the implementation of the ERP system, namely the automation of the balanced indicator system,

01:37:04.000 --> 01:37:12.000
then the audit and the implementation of the motivation system of personnel and the process of organizational changes,

01:37:12.000 --> 01:37:17.000
and finally, the implementation of the balanced indicator systems.

01:37:17.000 --> 01:37:19.000
The project results.

01:37:19.000 --> 01:37:29.000
The strategy of the company has been developed, there is no continuous adjustment and implementation of the strategy,

01:37:29.000 --> 01:37:37.000
the work of the balanced indicator system is integrated into the company's management processes,

01:37:37.000 --> 01:37:42.000
monitoring and control of the implementation of the target indicators is carried out,

01:37:42.000 --> 01:37:51.000
personal maps are used to set up tasks, that is, decomposition is carried out up to the level of the employee.

01:37:51.000 --> 01:37:56.000
Operational planning is ensured, pilot master plans are developed,

01:37:56.000 --> 01:38:06.000
the implementation of the ERP system for IT support of the balanced indicator system is currently nearing its end.

01:38:06.000 --> 01:38:11.000
What is the result for the client of this project?

01:38:11.000 --> 01:38:19.000
The growth of business turnover in accordance with the strategy of the group grew by $ 40 million per year

01:38:19.000 --> 01:38:26.000
during the first six months of the next year after the project was introduced.

01:38:26.000 --> 01:38:34.000
The shareholders are provided with transparency of the processes that flow into the business projects.

01:38:34.000 --> 01:38:41.000
Management of new projects is based on the strategy of the entire group of companies as a whole,

01:38:41.000 --> 01:38:46.000
and the interests of the top management are associated with the strategy of the group of companies

01:38:46.000 --> 01:38:50.000
through the implementation of the motivation system based on the results.

01:38:50.000 --> 01:38:56.000
The main result is the growth of the business value.

01:38:56.000 --> 01:39:02.000
Now let's see what happened at each stage of the development of the company strategy.

01:39:03.000 --> 01:39:06.000
