01:39:06.000 --> 01:39:14.000
First, the work with the company owners was carried out and the strategic goals of the company were determined.

01:39:14.000 --> 01:39:19.000
Then, within the framework of strategic diagnostics,

01:39:19.000 --> 01:39:28.000
