01:39:39.000 --> 01:39:51.000
The interests of stakeholders, in principle, interested groups, consumers, suppliers, competitors, employees of the state were identified.

01:39:52.000 --> 01:40:05.000
As a result, the vision was formed, the target state, which is expected by the company owners in the specified period, in five years.

01:40:06.000 --> 01:40:31.000
This target state was translated into the description of the strategy through the decomposition of goals by building a strategic map and the assignment of an indicator for each goal, which measures its achievements and target values.

01:40:31.000 --> 01:40:40.000
